This example will run under Windows 64. This FMU contains a model of the ExteriorWall of the Modelica Buildings library. The model is set-up with 5 state variables which are visible at the output ports. The Modelica model (ExteriorWallTotal.mo) as well as the FMU (Buildings_0Rooms_0Constructions_0Examples_0ExteriorWall.fmu) are both in the /test/auto folder.
Note: Remove the plotter to speed up the execution.
